AS to all three counts as amended:  Defendant was advised of constitutional rights and maximum penalties, and further advised that if not a United States citizen deportation is possible. Defendant examined as to plea, and entered a plea of guilty.  Court found defendant freely, voluntarily and intelligently waived all constitutional rights. Court found defendant guilty as charged in the AMENDED Information and ordered a Judgment of Conviction be entered into the record.  
Court adjourns sentencing to 8-27-2015.
